yingyinNormal.en: That is an excellent excellent question. That is excellent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是个非常好的问题，真的非常好。

yingyinNormal.en: Excellent! I'll go get my friends.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太棒了！我去叫我的朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: Excellent! Can I come into the out now?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好极了！放我出来吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Is that understood? Excellent. Fall out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 明白了吗？很好，解散。

yingyinNormal.en: It's around a dollar and most excellent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 售价一美元左右，用起来非常不错。

yingyinNormal.en: Me too. And me. Excellent. Thank you, Daddy Pig.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也是！还有我！ 非常好！谢谢你了，猪爸爸！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it is very good. Excellent tap. Excuse me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 非常棒。完美的自来水。不好意思。

yingyinNormal.en: But how were our seats? Excellent. I rest my case.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我俩的座位如何？相当好。那不就结了。

yingyinNormal.en: Excellent! It's in a cul-de-sac. We can box him in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太好了！在死胡同里，我们可以把他包饺子。

yingyinNormal.en: They're excellent company. Oh, do hold a ball! Kitty!
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们很好相处。噢，那就举办舞会！吉蒂！

yingyinNormal.en: I'm getting pretty good at this. Excellent. Good for me!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我进步神速。不错。我真行。

yingyinNormal.en: Excellent work, Francois, as usual. It's good, isn't it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 干得好，方师傅，一点都没变。很不错，对不对？

yingyinNormal.en: Hello. I'm Ben. We're gonna head straight over. Excellent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好，我是本。我们要马上过去。太好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Stills and Frank are excellent choices. Sol and Bender, sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯蒂尔和法兰克是很好的选择。教授，我选索尔和本德。

yingyinNormal.en: Excellent question. Though I wouldn't call it a war exactly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很好的问题，不过我不会称之为战争。

yingyinNormal.en: What a superbly featured room and what excellent boiled potatoes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多漂亮的房间啊，多漂亮的土豆啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that's excellent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是太好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr Collins, we are perfectly able to keep a cook. Excellent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们有钱请得起厨子。很棒。

yingyinNormal.en: Skylight? Okay, excellent. So you live in a house with a skylight?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天窗？太棒了，所以你住在一个有天窗的屋子里？

yingyinNormal.en: Excellent choice, Kevin. How much do you want to go for this time?
yingyinNormal.zh: 明智的选择 Kevin，你这次想买多少呢？
